        {
            "title": "港股開市︱收復兩萬五 恒指飆569點報25357點 騰訊高開逾4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場又憧憬中東戰火快將緩和，華爾街股市昨晚急彈，港股今早開市初段應聲向好，甫開市即收復兩萬五關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報25357點，升569點或2.3%。恒生科技指數開報4777點，升127點或2.75%；國企指數以8547點開市，升173點或2.07%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍揚升，滙控(00005)開報129.2元，升2.7%；友邦(01299)開報87.8元，升3.48%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報123.3元，升3.61%；騰訊(00700)甫開市即重越500元關口，以504元開市，升4.13%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">石油板塊則繼續回吐，中國海油(00883)開報27.32元，跌2.43%；中國石油(00857)開報10.6元，跌1.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">萬科企業(02202)去年虧損擴大至逾885億元人幣，但該股今早在競價時段仍報升，以2.94元開市，升1.03%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">零跑汽車(09863)獲董事長及股東於近期斥約2.3億元入市增持，該股今早開報48元，升2.08%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15821829-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e9%a3%86569%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125357%e9%bb%9e-%e9%a8%b0%e8%a8%8a%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b%e9%80%be4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 09:29:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
